Tableau Dashboards

Vaishnavi Shankar Devadig, 2024

Introduction¶

Leaving out the hundred other tableau Dashboards I have been creating, deleting, tweaking, hiding, at the moment, I want to show my dashboards on two things I love the most! - Indian Food and the legend himself, Shahrukh Khan!

** cries of joy **

Here are the two dashboards I would like to display for now. I will keep updating as and when my brain strikes a new idea and I decide to experiment with some new type of chart :)

Flavors of India

Tableau Link: https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/vaishnavi.devadig/viz/TheTasteofIndia/Dashboard1

  • The dashboard shows flavor profile of each state on hovering over the India Map.
  • It displays the relevance of vegetarianism in different regions.
  • The most used ingredients in Indian cooking.
  • The average prepping and cooking time.
  • The most prominent flavor in Indian cooking.

Shahrukh Khan Filmography

Tableau Link: https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/vaishnavi.devadig/viz/ShahrukhKhan_17077719601070/Dashboard1

  • The dashboard displays all the Shahrukh Khan-led movies by genre.
  • The first layer of the donut chart has genres.
  • The second layer has the movies under the selected genre.
  • The third has the total movie length for each genre.
  • The final layer extends for all those movies for which he has won a FilmFare India Award.
  • The line chart below shows the number of box office successes he has had in a year.
